{"tid":558443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"袁國勇料將轉H3N2　疫苗保護率跌至一成　續籲打針","createTime":"2018-02-12T09:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T09:45:01.000Z","uid":12856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"933b6c563cca668066d549358394213669ee0fe5","tid":558443,"uid":12856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"流感疫苗成效近日引起熱論。港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇於無綫節目《講清講楚》表示，現時正流行乙型流感病毒，今季疫苗保護率四成至七成，但稍後可能轉為流行甲型H3N2病毒，疫苗保護率將降至一成。他仍建議要打針，因疫苗對其他可能活躍的甲型流感病毒，有相當效用。<br />\n<br />\n至於是否因醫護人員接種率不高，令人對疫苗信心不足？袁國勇直言「最大問題是流感死亡率不夠高」：「醫護人員也是人，他們像覺得它們（流感）不是這麼嚴重。你在美國便知道，當地有州份立法，醫生和護士如不打流感疫苗不能上班。」他強調「每一個人命都重要」，呼籲市民不要因一、兩次疫苗不太有效，便覺得完全沒效。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇又強調，疫苗非常安全，副作用發生機會只有百萬分之二至三，但保護率通常達四成至七成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180211/s00001/1518336041499\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180211%2Fs00001%2F1518336041499&d=mG%2FCcgV8bzEAAY37QBwOIZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=dc08f16a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180211%2Fs00001%2F1518336041499&h=92bb6efe\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180211/s00001/1518336041499</a><br />\n<br />\n入錯貨散唔到?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b3bf083c34ce29bf8ac22d9fed6d6d4693ac417","tid":558443,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0248207ab5fe85038920f12b221793633fda86ed","tid":558443,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"財路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5061960dd3234202db19b1e9fcac30f3525b84d3","tid":558443,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b3bf083c34ce29bf8ac22d9fed6d6d4693ac417","tid":558443,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afaca4832a6aa8176778053d05cafc0f592c6b4c","tid":558443,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:42:21.000Z","msg":"袁國勇直言「最大問題是流感死亡率不夠高」<br />\n要幾高先唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7c6a027d1602b668a44dfd160254dd63d72c87","tid":558443,"uid":117837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"淫K反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}